            "title": "中聯重科發60億元人幣換股債 股價今早初段偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中聯重科(01157)公布，擬發行60億元人民幣的可換股債券；該股今早初段偏軟，最多曾跌逾3%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中聯重科官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01157-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中聯重科官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01157-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中聯重科官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早最低跌至8.13元，跌3.79%；截至上午約9時33分報8.33元，仍跌1.42%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述換股債為5年期，年息0.7%；初步換股價10.02元，較該股昨天收市價有溢價18.58%，較前30個交易日平均收市價8.007元更有溢價25.14%。</p>\n</div>",
