            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段變動不大，上證綜指以4155點開市，升4點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14332點，跌10點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升15點或0.32%，開報4733點；創業板指數開市報3322點，跌1點或0.03%。</p>\n</div>",
