        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段回吐 恒指跌199點報27627點 金沙中國低開近5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段回吐，恒生指數開市報27627點，跌199點或0.72%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報5853點，跌46點或0.79%；國企指數以9452點開市，跌60點或0.63%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金沙中國(01928)派發季績後，股價今早受壓，以17.9元開市，跌4.99%。新東方(09901)季度業績錄得增長，又上調全年營收預測，該股今早開報45.16元，升1.03%；同系東方甄選(01797)季度業績虧轉盈，該股今早開報22.5元，升1.81%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：金沙中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240909_FI_source-web_sands_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：金沙中國官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">多家公司趁市旺配股，股價今早多半低開。其中OSL集團(00863)開報17.18元，跌4.56%；Mirxes(02629)開報36.88元，暫時無升跌；嘉利國際(01050)開報2.61元，跌0.76%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">發盈喜的公司，股價今早則普遍造好。粵海投資(00270)開報7.21元，升1.12%；美聯集團(01200)開報2.66元，升0.76%；玖龍紙業(02689)開報8.57元，漲14.88%；山東墨龍(00568)開報4.36元，也升1.87%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15621035-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c199%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b127627%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%91%e6%b2%99%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 09:33:27",
